" bat viewer HAVE to be on the bottom
" fileviewer {*.md,*.txt,*.adoc,*.lua,*.csv,*.html,*.htm,*.java,*.kt,*.kts,*.sh,*.js,*.ts,*.css,*.scss,*.json,*.yml,*.yaml,*.toml} bat --color always --plain %c
fileviewer *[^/],.*[^/] bat --color always --plain %c

